OL,3,CPeople still suffering PTSD decades
OL,4,Cafter Troubles, study finds
OL,6,FThe legacy of the Troubles continues
OL,7,Fto impact on the mental health and
OL,8,Fwellbeing of people in Northern
OL,9,FIreland, a new study has concluded.
OL,11,FLed by researchers from Queen's
OL,12,FUniversity Belfast, the paper found
OL,13,Fthat current post-traumatic stress
OL,14,Fdisorder (PTSD) in those aged 50 and
OL,15,Fover in the region is as high as 4.74%.
OL,17,FThe research also highlights increased
OL,18,Flevels of depression, social
OL,19,Fdeprivation and harmful health
OL,20,Fbehaviours such as smoking and excess
OL,21,Falcohol in those with PTSD.
