OL,3,CPeople still suffering PTSD decades
OL,4,Cafter Troubles, study finds
OL,6,FThe study was jointly led by Dr Claire
OL,7,FPotter from the Centre for Public
OL,8,FHealth at Queen's alongside
OL,9,Fresearchers from Trinity College
OL,10,FDublin.
OL,12,FDr Potter was supervised by Professor
OL,13,FBernadette McGuinness, Professor Frank
OL,14,FKee and Professor Amy Jayne McKnight
OL,15,Ffrom Queen's.
