OL,3,CPeople still suffering PTSD decades
OL,4,Cafter Troubles, study finds
OL,6,FUsing data from the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FCohort for the Longitudinal study of
OL,8,FAgeing (Nicola), the study looked at
OL,9,Fmore than 2,000 people aged 50 and
OL,10,Fover from Northern Ireland who
OL,11,Freported a previous traumatic event.
OL,13,FAlmost 60% of those with PTSD reported
OL,14,Fthe Troubles as their worst traumatic
OL,15,Fexposure.
OL,17,FResearchers said this suggested long-
OL,18,Fterm consequences of the Troubles.
