OL,3,CPeople still suffering PTSD decades
OL,4,Cafter Troubles, study finds
OL,6,FIt also found that those with symptoms
OL,7,Fof current PTSD had worse memory
OL,8,Fperformance, were less likely to have
OL,9,Fcompleted higher educational degrees,
OL,10,Ftwice as likely to be single and more
OL,11,Fthan three times more likely to be
OL,12,Fliving in the most deprived areas of
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,15,FThe study said they were also more
OL,16,Flikely to have chronic and
OL,17,Fcardiovascular health conditions, to
OL,18,Fbe smokers and have lower levels of
OL,19,Fphysical activity and be more socially
OL,20,Fisolated.
