OL,3,CPeople still suffering PTSD decades
OL,4,Cafter Troubles, study finds
OL,6,FDr Potter said: "There is chronic
OL,7,Funderfunding of mental health in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland that does not match
OL,9,Fthe needs of our population.
OL,11,F"Commissioners need to support trauma
OL,12,Finformed training across health,
OL,13,Fsocial care and community sectors,
OL,14,Fintegrate lifestyle and social
OL,15,Fisolation interventions in our
OL,16,Fcommunities, address workforce gaps
OL,17,Fand continue to support large
OL,18,Fpopulation studies like Nicola that
OL,19,Fcan inform these policy decisions."
