OL,3,CPeople still suffering PTSD decades
OL,4,Cafter Troubles, study finds
OL,6,FProfessor McGuinness said: "This study
OL,7,Ffrom a representative sample of our
OL,8,Folder population in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fhighlights the ongoing impact of the
OL,10,FTroubles on our participants in terms
OL,11,Fof mental, cognitive and physical
OL,12,Fhealth.
OL,14,F"We call on policymakers to address
OL,15,Fthese gaps in service provision."
